org.eclipse.gef4.fx.swt.gestures

Class SWT2FXEventConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.gef4.fx.swt.gestures.SWT2FXEventConverter

  • public class SWT2FXEventConverter
extends java.lang.Object
    The SWT2FXEventConverter forwards SWT events to JavaFX. It is necessary because the FXCanvas does not forward gesture events and horizontal mouse wheel events.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description

      Represents the current SWT2FXEventConverter.GestureState of touch gesture interaction.
      protected static interface  SWT2FXEventConverter.ISceneRunnable
      The SWT2FXEventConverter.ISceneRunnable interface provides a callback method that is invoked in a privileged runnable on the JavaFX application thread.
